ivardefs.name: documentation
ivardefs.desc: Additional supporting documentation that explains the purpose of the group and the types of mappings within it.

ivardefs.name: extends
ivardefs.desc: Another group that this group adds rules to.

ivardefs.name: input_
ivardefs.desc: A name assigned to an instance of data. The instance must be provided when the mapping is invoked.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: A unique name for the group for the convenience of human readers.

ivardefs.name: rule_
ivardefs.desc: Transform Rule from source to target.

ivardefs.name: typeMode
ivardefs.desc: If this is the default rule set to apply for thie source type, or this combination of types.

properties.desc: Organizes the mapping into managable chunks for human review/ease of maintenance.
